		"description": {
			"value": "<p><em>Wondrous Item - Legendary (Requires Attunement)</em></p><p>This beetle-shaped medallion provides three benefits while it is on your person.</p><p><em><strong>Defense.</strong></em> You gain a +1 bonus to &amp;reference[Armor Class].</p><p><em><strong>Preservation.</strong></em> The scarab has 12 charges. If you fail a saving throw against a Necromancy spell or a harmful effect originating from an Undead, you can take a Reaction to expend 1 charge and turn the failed save into a successful one. The scarab crumbles into powder and is destroyed when its last charge is expended.</p><p><em><strong>Spell Resistance.</strong></em> You have Advantage on saving throws against spells.</p>",
